    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv that would help people using the `Hits` UI component, for sure !\r\n\r\nOn our side we have our own UI component but we could do the same as you propose, pass the `sendEvent` to children components.\r\nThe only concern is that we have a deep JSX tree before reaching the button that should trigger a `Conversion` event.\r\nMaybe a good workaround in this case is to put this sendEvent method in a homemade context.\r\n\r\nI am wondering if it could be interesting to provide this \"Insights context\" directly from `react-instantsearch-hook-web` package ?",
    "created_at": "2023-02-24T16:48:25Z",
