  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'd say it's probably best if you keep track of this in your own context, as for our use cases that wouldn't be needed, the component rendering has the same access as the place sendEvent is accessible from.\r\n\r\nIf you have some kind of indicator of scale and what makes the tree so complex that you can't use Hits, that would be interesting, as we'd like to encourage people to use the default components in most cases.",
