    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "In fact we do not use `Hits` because we have a custom UI for the listing of Hits, we do not want to use `ol` / `li` DOM nodes but instead we can use Table or Grid, depending the context.\r\n\r\nAs for passing the sendEvent across the tree, here is a shortlist of our tree component layers : \r\n- Grid component\r\n- Card\r\n- Modal\r\n- AddToCart\r\n- Button with onClick => sendEvent\r\n",
